# **Creating a charge**

1 - Create [asp.net](http://asp.net) app and set up shooting area.

2 - Download [stripe.net](http://stripe.net) using package manager 

3 - Using the quick start documentation. Copy and paste  the snippets for the charge form.

4 - Use the stripe api create a charge and output the charge id to the view.

Uso  de 2 keys. 1 publishable and 1 Secret

